title: How to make scrambled eggs.
text:
You take the eggs and take them out.
Then you get a nonstick pan and put the eggs in there. 
Add some butter
Whip that butter into the eggs.
Repeat three times.
Stir eggs constantly.
Remove.
Enjoy.

title: Grocery list
text:
gotta get these items:
eggs
butter
ribs (pork/beef)
potatoes
whatever you need.
